113419.Title: The Indian in the Cupboard
113419.title: The Indian in the Cupboard
113419.cast: Hal Scardino, Litefoot, Lindsay Crouse, Richard Jenkins, Rishi Bhat, Steve Coogan, David Keith, Sakina Jaffrey, Vincent Kartheiser, Nestor Serrano
113419.description: A boy receives a wooden cupboard, antique keys and an Iroquois warrior figurine for his birthday. The figurine comes to life overnight in the cabinet.
